      • getLogMessages

        public List<LogMessage> getLogMessages()
        The log occurred during the import - most of the times will be just the output logs

        NOTE: Logs are *not* stored here by Diversicon Core, applications need to call addLogMessage(LogMessage) explicitly.

        Since:

      • getLogMessages

        public List<LogMessage> getLogMessages(org.slf4j.event.Level level)
        Returns the logs occurred during the import having level higher or equal to the specified one.

        Most of the times the messages will be just the output logs

        NOTE: Logs are *not* stored here by Diversicon Core, applications need to call addLogMessage(LogMessage) explicitly.

        Since:
        0.1.0
